{
  "stem": "2581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this country, I bless three times a day, even though there were people here in this country that were against-- against helping our people when the knife was at their throat, when they being-- when they were being destroyed en masse, the thousands daily.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were organized from the government's side not to help our people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they must fight with everything they have for any-- any hatred and any prejudice.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because that could lead to everything-- I can't imagine that anything worse could be what-- than what happened to us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because many of our survivors wish that they wouldn't have survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because this is how-- how you feel after going through what-- what we did.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I know from the-- the actions that the parents have taken with their children [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that they're going in the right direction, that they're good people.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father used to-- told me under my bar mitzvah [NON-ENGLISH], which means to be observant Jew in the house and to be a decent person, human being.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think they are both, they are Jews and human beings on the street and in the house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But what I-- what I wanted to add-- what I wanted to add-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] was the fact that I have six children, six grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I keep thinking if two people like us could have six children, those that were killed wasn't just the number that were killed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Multiply this by all these six numbers, at least minimum of six.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were so many more millions killed than the numbers actually imply.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And yet, there are people that are trying to deny it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I am not worried about these deniers.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
